The Abipones, as I told you before, are des- titute of beard, and have perfectly smooth chins like all the other Indians, both of whose parents are Americans. If you see an Indian with a little beard, you may conclude, without hesi- tation, that one os his parents or at any ratchis grandfather, must have been of European ex- traction.
